# ============================================
# OCULUS SANTÉ - ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# ============================================
# This file shows all available environment variables.
# Copy this to .env.local for local development if needed.
# For Vercel production, these are OPTIONAL.

# --------------------------------------------
# OPTIONAL: Basic Authentication (Preview Only)
# --------------------------------------------
# Uncomment and set these if you want to password-protect
# preview deployments. If not set, the site is publicly accessible.
# 
# BASIC_AUTH_USER=your_username
# BASIC_AUTH_PASS=your_password

# --------------------------------------------
# NOTES FOR CLIENT
# --------------------------------------------
# - The production site does NOT require any environment variables
# - All configuration is built into the code
# - Basic auth is only useful for protecting preview/staging URLs
# - Leave these commented out for a fully public website
